data.description: Incredible opportunity to own a charming property on the private Sunrise Beach. This home has mesmerizing water views, its own private sandy beach, and a solid sea wall. The first floor includes an open concept living room, with the dining and kitchen areas that lead to an expansive deck overlooking the ocean, ideal for entertainment. The living room has maple hardwood floors, a gas fireplace, and a built-in bookcase. The kitchen has abundant cabinetry, new appliances, granite countertops and tile floors. A full bathroom completes the first floor. 3 bedrooms and a half bathroom with French porcelain floor tiles, are on the second floor. The master bedroom has breathtaking ocean views and plenty of natural sunlight. This home has rolling hurricane & plantation shutters, a full basement, walk-in cedar closet, & laundry room. It's move-in ready! Suitable for someone who is looking for a primary residence, or an investment property. Tour this gorgeous beach-side retreat before it’s gone!
